

Welcome to the Simple-Seam-Project-With-Maven wiki!

In order to run the sample, please make sure you have a mySQL database up & running, and a valid mysql-connector in your Tomcat lib folder

Execute the following commands to create the database :

mysql -u root
create database seamdemo;
CREATE USER 'seamdemo@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'seamdemo';
GRANT ALL ON seamdemo.* TO 'seamdemo'@'localhost'

